Object Properties Configuration:
Use case: Control property behavior.

let user = {};
Object.defineProperty(user, "name", {value:"John", writable:false});


Property Flags and Descriptors:
Use case: View property attributes.

let desc = Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor({x:1}, "x");
console.log(desc.writable); // true


Property Getters and Setters:
Use case: Define computed properties.

let user = {
  first:"John", last:"Doe",
  get full(){ return this.first + " " + this.last; }
};
console.log(user.full); // John Doe
